different station.

00:16:52.200 --> 00:16:55.170 align:middle line:84%
You talk on your cell phone,
which can go through walls.

00:16:55.170 --> 00:16:57.150 align:middle line:84%
Magnetic fields
goes through walls,

00:16:57.150 --> 00:16:59.370 align:middle line:84%
that's how it picks up the
signal from the cell phone

00:16:59.370 --> 00:17:00.420 align:middle line:90%
tower.

00:17:00.420 --> 00:17:04.710 align:middle line:84%
That's how we are picking
up each other's hearts.

00:17:04.710 --> 00:17:08.910 align:middle line:84%
And what we feel
is radiated through

00:17:08.910 --> 00:17:11.710 align:middle line:90%
