00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:15.069 align:middle line:84%
If we feel love, care,
appreciation, kindness,

00:17:15.069 --> 00:17:17.880 align:middle line:84%
compassion, what have
been called the uplifting

00:17:17.880 --> 00:17:20.339 align:middle line:84%
qualities of the heart,
the renewing, regenerating

00:17:20.339 --> 00:17:23.490 align:middle line:84%
qualities, that creates
the program that goes out.

00:17:23.490 --> 00:17:26.700 align:middle line:84%
And actually in
our lab, we've been

00:17:26.700 --> 00:17:29.130 align:middle line:84%
able to see that
that pattern shows up

00:17:29.130 --> 00:17:35.070 align:middle line:84%
in the brain waves of people
standing three feet away not

00:17:35.070 --> 00:17:36.150 align:middle line:90%
